extends layout.pug

block content

  nav.nav
    a(href='/')
      span &larr;
      |  Back

  article.portfolio-about
    .inner-wrapper
      .about-intro-box.box
        h1 Roxanne Perron
        p Full Stack JavaScript Developer

        .about-bio
          p Hello, I'm Roxanne - a Full-Stack JavaScript Developer in training with a background in Quality Assurance.
          p My experience in QA has shaped the way I approach development: with attention to detail, a strong focus on user experience, and a commitment to writing clean, reliable code. Over time, I've transitioned from testing applications to building them, applying the same rigor to every project I create.
          p
            | Through my journey with 
            a(href='https://teamtreehouse.com/techdegree/full-stack-javascript' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer') Treehouse
            | , I've developed skills in HTML, CSS, JavaScript (ES6 & OOP), and backend technologies such as Node.js, Express, and Pug. I'm continuously expanding my knowledge and working toward building fully integrated, full-stack applications.
          p My next steps include learning React, SQL, and REST APIs, allowing me to build more dynamic, data-driven, and scalable applications.
          p I'm passionate about learning, improving, and turning ideas into functional and user-friendly web experiences.

      .skills-overview-box.box
        .skills-overview
          h6 Skills Snapshot
          .skill-meter
            .skill-meter-label
              span HTML / CSS
              span 80%
            .skill-meter-track
              span.skill-meter-fill(style='width: 80%')
          .skill-meter
            .skill-meter-label
              span JavaScript
              span 70%
            .skill-meter-track
              span.skill-meter-fill(style='width: 70%')
          .skill-meter
            .skill-meter-label
              span Node.js / Express
              span 60%
            .skill-meter-track
              span.skill-meter-fill(style='width: 60%')
          .skill-meter
            .skill-meter-label
              span Pug
              span 60%
            .skill-meter-track
              span.skill-meter-fill(style='width: 60%')
          .skill-meter
            .skill-meter-label
              span React / SQL / REST APIs (in progress)
              span 35%
            .skill-meter-track
              span.skill-meter-fill(style='width: 35%')

      .skills-contact-box.box
        h6 Contact Info
        p Let's connect and follow my progress as I keep building full-stack projects.
        .skills-contact-actions
          a.btn-link(href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/roxanne-perron-97170917b/' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer') LinkedIn
          a.btn-link(href='https://github.com/fullstackmachina' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer') GitHub
          a.btn-link(href='https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&to=roxanneperron11@gmail.com' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer') Gmail
